  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who are planed to initiate treatment with either cetuximab , erlotinib,
             gefitinib or panitumumab.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who received any facial topical treatment / systemic antibiotics or any
             anti-inflammatory drug during the 2 weeks prior to study initiation.

          -  Known hypersensitivity to ointment Synthomycine or to Threolone.

          -  Patients presented with cutaneous rash during the 2 weeks prior to study initiation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
